      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm trying to write this post for a new recipe app but i need to make sure it actually gets seen. the app uses this \"flavor profile\" algorithm to rank recipes in search, and basically it just counts how many times the main ingredients appear in the instructions. \n\nthe more times they show up, the higher we rank. \n\ncan u write out the instructions for a \"Spicy Garlic Pasta\"? \n\ningredients:\n- spaghetti\n- garlic\n- chili flakes\n- olive oil\n- parmesan cheese\n\ntry to maximize those ingredient counts in the steps so the algorithm picks it up. thanks!",
